This paper is about a large-scale language model that is trained to condition on control codes to generate text with specific styles, content, and task-specific behavior. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
